matlabpool('open',2); % double threaded 

caseTag='ANHA4-ENG1';
dataP=sprintf('/lustre/home/breith/ANHA4/%s-S',caseTag);

timeTag = sprintf('%s/flistname_%s.txt',dataP,caseTag);
timeTag = importdata(timeTag);

%for ii=1:size(timeTag,1) % NB. This loop could be //ized
parfor ii=1:size(timeTag,1) % This is //ized
 gridTFile=[dataP,caseTag,'_',timeTag{ii},'_gridT.nc']
 votemper=double(GetNcVar(gridTFile,'votemper'));
 vosaline=double(GetNcVar(gridTFile,'vosaline'));
 ssh=double(GetNcVar(gridTFile,'sossheig'));
 mld=double(GetNcVar(gridTFile,'somxl010'));

 ha=tight_subplot(2,2)
 axes(1); surface(votemper); colorbar ; 
 text(0.02,0.98,'TEM'); text(0.90,0.02,timeTag{ii})
 axes(2); surface(vosaline); colorbar ; 
 text(0.02,0.98,'SAL'); text(0.90,0.02,timeTag{ii})
 axes(3); surface(ssh); colorbar ; 
 text(0.02,0.98,'SSH'); text(0.90,0.02,timeTag{ii})
 axes(4); surface(mld); colorbar ; 
 text(0.02,0.98,'MLD'); text(0.90,0.02,timeTag{ii})
 
 export_fig(sprintf('Figs/monitoring_%s.png',timeTag))
end
